			Point of Interest

	*Sharpthorne : it is the main area, concentrated in the eastern part and towards the center and north of the continent. It is separated from the second area, to 
the north by a high mountain that descends to the northwest. In the west to the south, the territory is crossed by several rivers, making the passage in this region 
no longer through portals or through NPC teleporters, but by traversing these rivers by flight or by other methods. Is de second biggest area of the region.
		*Bayswick : located in the east of the region, is a big city with a big port.
		*Irvien Stable : located in the extreme north point of the area is a mount stable.
		*Silverhammer Harbour : located in the east, as an extension of the city.
	*Azurr Forest : This area is the largest and most extensive in the region. It covers the northeast of the territory, along the "Sharpthorne" area beyond the 
mountain, extends in the west and descends in the south, surrounding the entire continental part of this area. It has access to water to the north and west and the 
whole area is covered by forests of trees with wide branches. Moreover, it is crossed by several rivers, all of which intersect in the southwest, reaching the 
"Outland Ocean" forming here a big bay.
		*Greencoast Wharf : a small port located in southwest, where all the rivers intersect.
		*Red Flue Stable : is a tavern located in the north-east of the area close to the shore.
		*Anjan's Green Stable : is a tavern located on a meadow, in south of the area.
		*Primrose Lake : located in west-center of the area with a small pier. Two rivers flow into this lake, through waterfalls, and form a single one at the 
		exit from this lake, heading south.
			*Vygor Port : located in north-west of the area, a small port from where can be rented boats to go to the island.
	*Sunnymead Island : it is the third area of the region, the smallest but still big, and is separated from the mainland by a rift in the ground that separates this
area from the mainland, and water flows here from the "Outland Ocean". This water is not very wide and the passage from the continental area can be crossed with 
flying mounts, with small boats that can be rented from the port or by swimming.
		*North High Peak : located in north-east, is one of two peaks of the mountain.
		*South Ram Port : located in the south-east of the island from where people can cross the big river to go back to the continent.
		*Gryveer Field : located in the west side, this NPC build here a farm and protected it from surrounding monsters with other two friends and his wife.